description:
SATanic is a store of value built on the Ethereum blockchain with deflationary characteristics. Whenever $SATANIC is transferred, 2% of the amount is burned. This built in self destructive functionality increases the assets scarcity over time, and is hard coded directly into our monetary structure.
SATanic is based on the design of the Bomb token – the original hyper deflationary, self-destructing currency.
name: SATANIC
